title: Happy Hour Halloween Special - Resident Evil (feat. Avalanche Reviews, Carrier)
description:
Since its the night of horror, we're adding a touch of survival to it with an in-depth retrospective on the entire Resident Evil game series. Expect a whole lot of zombies, boulder punching and nostalgia as we go from the series humble roots to its blockbuster heights. 

Subscribe to Avalanche Reviews: https://www.youtube.com/@AvalancheReviews
Subscribe to Carrier: A Raccoon City Story: https://www.youtube.com/@carrieraraccooncitystory
